data.name: HelpLbl.Text
data.value:
Your objective in Cloud Pong (ping pong) game is to score points by hitting the ball with your paddle and prevent the ball from passing your side of the screen. The game ends when you reach 10 points or when you decide to stop playing.
Controls:
Use the up arrow key to move your paddle up. Use the down arrow key to move your paddle down.
Gameplay:
Start the game by pressing the "Start" button on the Home screen.
Once the game starts, control your paddle using the up and down arrow keys. Your goal is to hit the ball with your paddle and send it back to the opponent's side.
Each time you successfully hit the ball and it passes the opponent's paddle, you will score a point.
Be careful not to miss hitting the ball, as it will result in your opponent scoring a point.
The game will continue until a player reaches 10 points or when you decide to quit.
You can pause the game at any time by pressing the space bar. This will temporarily freeze the game and allow you to take a break. Press the space bar again to resume the game.
Enjoy the game and strive to beat your opponent's score!
